long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Looking for a fun and unique way to show your support for Bitcoin on Twitter? Look no further than the Bitcoin Twitter Fix extension! This handy tool replaces the standard Twitter logo with a Bitcoin logo, giving your Twitter feed a whole new look and feel.

With the Bitcoin Twitter Fix, you can show your love for Bitcoin in a subtle yet eye-catching way. Whether you're a Bitcoin enthusiast or just a fan of the cryptocurrency world, this extension is the perfect way to customize your Twitter experience.

So why wait? Download the Bitcoin Twitter Fix today and start showing off your love for Bitcoin on Twitter!
